Name: Zombies Must Die
About the game: Zombies must die is a pile of fun! In a bunch of manually created locations, you need to shoot all kinds of zombies in order to collect the documents left in this infected lab. To do this there is a huge arsenal of firearms that are necessary to blow up the zombie's brain (pun), Zombies must die provides a fun retro shooting from start to finish.
